# Dinosaur Base Behavior Tree Blueprint
# This is a blueprint asset file that would be created in the Unreal Editor
# The actual implementation would be done through the visual node editor

# ROOT STRUCTURE:
# Root
# └── Selector (Main Behavior Selector)
#     ├── Sequence (Emergency Behaviors) [Priority 1]
#     │   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (Safety < 30)
#     │   └── Task: Flee to Safety
#     ├── Sequence (Critical Needs) [Priority 2]
#     │   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (Thirst < 20)
#     │   └── Task: Find Water Source
#     ├── Sequence (Basic Needs) [Priority 3]
#     │   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (Hunger < 30)
#     │   └── Task: Forage for Food
#     ├── Sequence (Social Behaviors) [Priority 4]
#     │   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (IsSocialSpecies = true AND Social < 40)
#     │   └── Task: Seek Social Interaction
#     ├── Sequence (Domesticated Behaviors) [Priority 5]
#     │   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (DomesticationLevel > 50)
#     │   └── Selector (Domesticated Actions)
#     │       ├── Task: Follow Bonded Player
#     │       ├── Task: Stay Near Base
#     │       └── Task: Perform Trained Behavior
#     └── Selector (Default Behaviors) [Priority 6]
#         ├── Sequence (Personality-Based)
#         │   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (Personality = Curious)
#         │   └── Task: Investigate Surroundings
#         ├── Sequence (Territorial)
#         │   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (Personality = Territorial)
#         │   └── Task: Patrol Territory
#         └── Task: Idle Behavior

# SERVICES (attached to main selector):
# - Update Needs Service (every 5 seconds)
# - Memory Management Service (every 30 seconds)
# - Player Detection Service (every 2 seconds)
# - Threat Assessment Service (every 3 seconds)

# BLACKBOARD KEYS USED:
# - CurrentBehaviorState (Enum)
# - Hunger (Float 0-100)
# - Thirst (Float 0-100)
# - Energy (Float 0-100)
# - Social (Float 0-100)
# - Safety (Float 0-100)
# - DomesticationLevel (Float 0-100)
# - IsSocialSpecies (Bool)
# - Personality (Enum)
# - TargetLocation (Vector)
# - TargetActor (Object)
# - PlayerActor (Object)
# - LastKnownPlayerLocation (Vector)
# - ThreatLevel (Float)
# - IsNocturnal (Bool)
# - CurrentTimeOfDay (Float 0-24)

# This file represents the structure that would be created in the UE5 Behavior Tree Editor
# The actual visual nodes and connections would be configured through the editor interface